Author: mayaaaa16
Text: I say eat that cake, birthdays and holidays don't count

Author: Arceliaz
Text: Happy birthday! ❤️  Don’t put pressure on yourself to suddenly be able to let go of this stuff for the day. It’s harder to break a habit than it is to just let it run it’s course. Maybe do some other nice self care things that aren’t food focused to celebrate 😊   And have fun clubbing!!
